                <h2>Marios R. Belk</h2>
                <p class="lead">
                    Lecturer at the <a href="https://www.uclancyprus.ac.cy" target="_blank">University of Central Lancashire (Cyprus Campus)</a>
                </p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;">
                    I am also a Research Associate at the <a href="http://www.cs.ucy.ac.cy" target="_blank">Department of Computer Science</a>, <a href="http://www.ucy.ac.cy/en/" target="_blank">University of Cyprus</a> where I completed my PhD in December 2015 under the supervision of <a href="http://www.cs.ucy.ac.cy/~cssamara/" target="_blank">Professor George Samaras</a>.
                </p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;">
                    My research interests include Cyber Security with focus on Usable Security, User Authentication, Human Interaction Proofs, Password Managers, Security in Mixed Reality, User Experience, Eye-tracking, User Modeling, Personalization, Cognition.
                </p>
